description: packages/rpg-engine 纯引擎边界\\nglobs: packages/rpg-engine/**\\nalwaysApply: false\\n---\\n\\n# 引擎包边界（rpg-engine）\\n\\n详情：[05](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/05-技术选型与工程边界.md)、[19](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)、[02](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md)。\\n\\n## 必须执行\\n\\n- **禁止** import：`react`、`react-dom`、`next`、`@xyflow/*`。\\n- **禁止** `window` / `document` / `localStorage`（测试可注入）。\\n- **EngineHost 单例**由 server/壳持有；本包提供 create/host API。\\n- **CallSession** 在 Host 内存；`frozenCard`；同 user 通话互斥。\\n- Composer 只读；EffectExecutor 仅出口/Free 管线；工具只登记 candidate。\\n- **FreeCallPostPipeline** 为 Free 挂机唯一总入口（可注入）；v1 = 有效门闩 + MemoryCommit +（有 candidate 则 ExitSelector）；禁 transcript 隐式扫描。\\n- Free Session.`packageId  [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":115,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-969cfc14-4ffe-4f6c-a35c-a2469c0c9887-20\\nfc_b5d6edd3-d965-94f8-86ea-b159bf8924eb_5\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/README.md\"}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-969cfc14-4ffe-4f6c-a35c-a2469c0c9887-20\\nfc_b5d6edd3-d965-94f8-86ea-b159bf8924eb_5\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784786275120\"},\"model_call_id\":\"e8d790a1-93fd-4d56-9a3d-1b6a957221fb-4-jbx6\",\"session_id\":\"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784786275071}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":116,"content":"[gbx] · 读取 packages/rpg-engine/README.md","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":117,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-969cfc14-4ffe-4f6c-a35c-a2469c0c9887-20\\nfc_b5d6edd3-d965-94f8-86ea-b159bf8924eb_5\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/README.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"# @airpc/rpg-engine\\n\\n纯 TypeScript 引擎包（准 npm）。**不依赖** `react` / `next` / `@xyflow/*`，也不承载具体磁盘/数据库实现。\\n\\n存取数据请注入 **Port**（存/取 callback）。协议说明见：\\n\\n→ **[引擎存取 Port 与 IO 适配（技术设计 23）](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)**\\n\\n本机 Studio 的默认 IO 实现在：`apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`（不要从浏览器代码引用）。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 安装与入口\\n\\n```ts\\nimport {\\n  createEngineHost,\\n  getEngineHost,\\n  type MemoryPort,\\n  type ProfilePort,\\n  type ContentPort,\\n  type EngineLogPort,\\n  type WorkspaceSnapshot,\\n  type PackageValidateBundle,\\n} from \\\"@airpc/rpg-engine\\\";\\n```\\n\\n只从包名导入；不要深挖 `src/host/...`。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 最短用法（本机）\\n\\n1. 用 IO 模块创建 ports（Studio：`engineIOModule` 工厂，指向 `data/`）。  \\n2. `createEngineHost({ ...ports })` 注入。  \\ [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":121,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nV2-IO-11 requires \",\"session_id\":\"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784786281697}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":123,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\"engine-boundaries, and\",\"session_id\":\"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784786281698}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":124,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\" AGENTS. Specific issues\",\"session_id\":\"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784786281698}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":130,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\" and engine-boundaries\",\"session_id\":\"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784786281698}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":134,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nAGENTS iron rules still state Memory equals SQLite without mentioning Port or engineIOModule. codingRole.mdc may be outdated. 19 might st