cd1187f19d_3\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md\",\"offset\":180,\"limit\":100},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"\\n- 调试只读**已保存** Content；`beginCall` 写入 `frozenCard` + `composeScene`（本地时间 / 方向）→ Composer → `renderedPrompt`。\\n- 发现问题：退出调试 → 回画布修改并保存 → 再开调试。调试器内**不提供**改卡 UI。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 3. Content 工作区磁盘布局\\n\\n创建故事包 = 在硬盘上新建目录 `data/storis-packages/<packageId>/`。  \\n**大故事按文件拆开**：包配置一份、每张卡一个文件；禁止把全部卡内联进单一巨型 JSON 作为编辑真源。\\n\\n```text\\ndata/\\n  workspace.json\\n  characters/\\n    <agentId>.json\\n  tools/\\n    registry.json                 # 非真源／预留导出；ToolRegistry v1 = 代码 builtinRegistry（见需求 13）\\n  assets/\\n    meta/<assetId>.json           # 全局资产元数据真源（见需求 14）\\n    files/...\\n  storis-packages/                    # 故事包根目录正式名（拼写定稿；全仓改名另立项）\\n    <packageId>/                      # 例：golden_handoff/\\ [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":150,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-6cf0338c-e7e8-4724-adc7-66975adae922-25\\nfc_f3dacc40-6f52-9375-b1d9-cdcd1187f19d_4\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/20-记忆存储与投影.md\",\"offset\":180,\"limit\":50}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-6cf0338c-e7e8-4724-adc7-66975adae922-25\\nfc_f3dacc40-6f52-9375-b1d9-cdcd1187f19d_4\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784786285066\"},\"model_call_id\":\"e8d790a1-93fd-4d56-9a3d-1b6a957221fb-5-g9kt\",\"session_id\":\"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784786285005}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":151,"content":"[gbx] · 读取 docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/20-记忆存储与投影.md","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":154,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-6cf0338c-e7e8-4724-adc7-66975adae922-25\\nfc_f3dacc40-6f52-9375-b1d9-cdcd1187f19d_4\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/20-记忆存储与投影.md\",\"offset\":180,\"limit\":50},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"\\n4. 空结果 → []；包装层可附 hint「放宽时间或换关键词」\\n\\n5. 查询预算建议 ≤200～500ms；超时 → 工具错误\\n```\\n\\n**query 规范化：** trim；过短（如 1 字）可拒或强制要时间窗；去无意义引号；转义 FTS 特殊字符。中文 v1 可整句 MATCH，效果差再加分词/片段 OR。\\n\\n**降级：** 无 FTS 时用 `LIKE '%'||q||'%'` + 同上过滤 + LIMIT；生产路径以 FTS 为准。\\n\\n### 5.5 与热层 / rollup\\n\\n| 路径 | 何时 | 读什么 |\\n|------|------|--------|\\n| `projectForCall` | beginCall | 最近 N/M + 近 1～2 rollup，有字符预算 |\\n| `search_memory` | 通话中 FC | 条件查 entries（及可选 rollup），LIMIT≤10 |\\n| `rollupIfNeeded` | Commit 后 | 当前月/季 + 上一自然月/季缺失补算（有界） |\\n\\n`search` **不依赖**先有 rollup；可直接命中很老的 `call_summary`。\\n\\n### 5.6 审计\\n\\n`data/logs/*.jsonl`：工具名、参数摘要、hit 数、耗时；可记 id，不强制记全文。\\n\\n## 6. 迁移与演进\\n\\n- SQLite → Postgres：换 MemoryPort 实现，表语义保持（FTS → 对应 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":160,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nChecking V2-IO-11 \",\"session_id\":\"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784786292485}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":186,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nAGENTS iron rules should mention Port and engineIOModule. Document 05's Persistence row uses outdated naming. docs-execution should add 23 to the Host/IO reading list. codingRole persistence wording may also be outdated.\",\"session_id\":\"54731ed0-b797-4648-ab4c-b3b5d1ebe8bc\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784786295951}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":188,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-f08d0395-ad97-4dc3-aacd-c97bfc8cacef-27\\nfc_38c00a55-0651-92bb-87db-99a4c08913c7_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎