SQLite、文本 LLM 在 server；本机 IO = engineIOModule |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":16,"content":"| [20-记忆存储与投影.md](./20-记忆存储与投影.md) | **Memory 投影/rollup/FTS**；Sqlite 实现在 engineIOModule；引擎只认 MemoryPort |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":19,"content":"| [23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md) | **存取 Port 协议；本机 IO 在 studioV2/engineIOModule；禁引擎内 fs/sqlite 实现** |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/20-记忆存储与投影.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":5,"content":"> **结论：** Content = JSON 文件；**Memory = SQLite**（经 `MemoryPort`）。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":6,"content":"> **实现落点：** Sqlite 适配在 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/memory/`；引擎只认 `MemoryPort` 契约，**不**内置 `better-sqlite3`。协议见 [23 §4.1](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":13,"content":"| 故事包 / 角色 Def / 卡 / 资产 meta | JSON 文件 | 作者向、可 diff；经 ContentPort |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":14,"content":"| Profile 薄存档（Board、story 变量、research、schedule…） | JSON `profile.save.json` | **不含**万级 episodic 数组；经 ProfilePort |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":15,"content":"| NPC 记忆条目 + rollup | **SQLite** | 按 userId+agentId 索引查询；经 MemoryPort |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":26,"content":"壳侧可换路径与介质；引擎只认 MemoryPort，不硬编码上表路径。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":96,"content":"  → MemoryPort.projectForCall({ userId, agentId, nowIso })","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":140,"content":"  → MemoryPort.search（userId/agentId 由 Host 注入，忽略模型伪造）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":206,"content":"- SQLite → Postgres：换 MemoryPort 实现（本机默认在 `engineIOModule`；壳可自带），表语义保持（FTS → 对应全文索引）  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":7,"content":"**存取：** Host 经注入的 Content / Profile / Memory / EngineLog Port 访问工作区；磁盘布局由 IO 模块解释。本机实现见 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`（详见 [23](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":17,"content":"  → createEngineIOPorts(dataRoot)     # Studio：engineIOModule","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":19,"content":"  → loadWorkspace（经 ContentPort）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":25,"content":"  → ProfilePort / MemoryPort 持久化（非引擎内直写 fs）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":40,"content":"  /** 规则在引擎；读包经 ContentPort.loadPackageForValidate（见 23 §7） */","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":46,"content":"  /** 门禁选定后，后续 API 带此上下文或显式传 userId；落盘经 ProfilePort */","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":189,"content":"> **布局真源在本文；谁读谁写见 [23](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)。** Host / 引擎只调 Port，**不**拼接下列路径。本机路径解释属 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":270,"content":"- Workspace 加载：`loadWorkspace` 经 ContentPort 装入 `scheduleCards`（本机 IO 扫 `characters/schedule-cards/*`）；**禁止**创建或 load `storis-packages/__schedule__/`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":324,"content":"4. 经 EngineLogPort 写 jsonl + 经 ProfilePort save Profile","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":478,"content":"| `data/logs/engine-YYYYMMDD.jsonl` | 事件 + error；**旁路**，不整份塞进 SaveGame；**持久化只经 EngineLogPort**（[23 §4.4](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":481,"content":"**WET 与 Profile：** 逻辑事件只走 ring + EngineLogPort→jsonl；**禁止**把整份 WET 写入薄 Profile／SaveGame。幂等权威在通话内 `CallSession.effectLedger`。Studio 受控追加仅 `wet.annotation`／`wet.compensation`（标注／补偿说明），**只追加不改写**既有行，禁止借追加篡改 effect 历史。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/18-部署拓扑与BS架构.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":19,"content":"  · 不内置 fs/sqlite 实现；本机实现见 apps/studioV2/engineIOModule","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":31,"content":"| Next 门面 | 注入 userId、校验、调 Host、HTTP 映射；**装配 engineIOModule → Host** | 剧情规则 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":33,"content":"| engineIOModule（Studio 本机） | JSON+fs、SQLite、jsonl 等 Port 实现 | 剧情规则、Client 引用 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":43,"content":"| 故事包 / 角色 / 资产 | JSON（`storis-packages/`、`characters/`、`assets/`） | ContentPort → 本机 `engineIOModule` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":44,"content":"| 薄 SaveGame | `data/users/<userId>/profile.save.json` | ProfilePort → 同上 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":45,"content":"| **Memory DB** | `data/memory/memory.sqlite`（见 [20](./20-记忆存储与投影.md)） | MemoryPort → 同上 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":46,"content":"| 日志 | `data/logs/engine-YYYYMMDD.jsonl` | EngineLogPort → 同上 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":47,"content":"| 黄金样例 | `data/storis-packages/golden_handoff/` | 经 ContentPort |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":67,"content":"错误体统一 `{ ok, code, message, details? }`（[19 §15](./19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)）。写成功路径由门面调 Host（经 ProfilePort / Content 编辑 BFF）；**禁止**在 API 层绕过 Port 直写引擎以为真源的经历态。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":79,"content":"| POST | `/api/stories/[packageId]/validate` | 是 | `validatePackage`（规则见 [08](../需求/08-内容校验规则.md)；读包经 ContentPort，见 [23 §7](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":99,"content":"- [ ] client 无引擎写口、无 engineIOModule；LLM Key 仅 server","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":101,"content":"- [ ] 工作区经 Port：Content JSON + 薄 Profile JSON + **Memory SQLite**；layout 旁车不进运行（实现见 engineIOModule）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":6,"content":"> **一句话：** 引擎只声明「要什么 / 存什么」的 Port 协议；具体落盘由外部 IO 模块响应。本机默认实现物理落在 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":16,"content":"| Studio V2 / 本机 Next | `engineIOModule`：JSON+fs + SQLite + jsonl |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":30,"content":"  ↓ 装配：createEngineIOPorts(dataRoot) → createEngineHost({ ports })","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":33,"content":"apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/（本机 IO 实现）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":38,"content":"- **引擎禁止** import `engineIOModule` 或 `node:fs` / `better-sqlite3` **实现**。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":39,"content":"- **Client 禁止** import `engineIOModule`（与 Client/Server 隔离规则一致）。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":50,"content":"5. **类型真源**：Port 接口与 DTO 定义在 `packages/rpg-engine`；`engineIOModule` 可 import 引擎类型，反向禁止。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":64,"content":"### 4.1 MemoryPort","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":67,"content":"**本机实现：** SQLite（原 `createSqliteMemoryPort` → `engineIOModule/memory`）。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":71,"content":"interface MemoryPort {","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":125,"content":"### 4.2 ProfilePort","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":132,"content":"interface ProfilePort {","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":173,"content":"### 4.3 ContentPort","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":196,"content":"interface ContentPort {","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":287,"content":"### 4.4 EngineLogPort","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":294,"content":"interface EngineLogPort {","contentTruncated":false,