\":822144,\"cacheWriteTokens\":0}}\n433:先读取并严格执行该 prompt 文件。按 batch-exe 流程执行：先读技能与执行索引中的 V2-IO-11。V2-IO-11 是文档收口。正在对照必读文档与现状，找出需回写处。正在扫描需回写的过期表述。多数文档似已部分更新；继续精读关键段落，找残留过期表述。继续深挖仍把「引擎直写 fs/sqlite」当真源的表述。核对现网代码与文档残留不一致处，并开始回写。开始回写残留过期句，使 18/19/20、规则与 AGENTS 与技术设计 23 对齐。文档已回写。正在跑 `quality:engine` 与 `quality:studio` 验证。验证已通过，正在将 V2-IO-11 标为 ✅。**V2-IO-11 已完成**（文档收口）。\n442:**Verify：** `quality:engine` ✅ · `quality:studio` ✅  \n443:**索引：** V2-IO-11 ⬜ → ✅（未动 STATE.json；未做 V2-IO-12）\n444:[gbx] ■ executor:V2-IO-11 done exit=0 elapsed=272s\n==== index line ====\n118:V2-IO-11  回写 18/19/20、engine-boundaries、AGENTS 过期句\n150:| ✅ | V2-IO-11 | **文档收口**：18/19/20、engine-boundaries、AGENTS、README 用法与 23 交叉链接一致 | true |\n","localExecutionTimeMs":106},"isBackground":false}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-5156ac2c-1d36-4580-a80b-7f6f97c3e965-31\nfc_84704f4b-a054-9a83-b992-408f0f83f98a_4","startedAtMs":"1784786589814","completedAtMs":"1784786590323"},"model_call_id":"37c577a3-d489-4424-8aef-203754da5572-6-711l","session_id":"af9c32ce-fb63-495c-a8c5-233eb47f1680","timestamp_ms":1784786590460}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-5156ac2c-1d36-4580-a80b-7f6f97c3e965-32\nfc_84704f4b-a054-9a83-b992-408f0f83f98a_5","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","offset":1,"limit":60},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 19. 引擎宿主、CallSession 与工作区（技术定稿）\n\n相关：[00-文档索引](../需求/00-文档索引.md) · [02-运行时协议](../需求/02-运行时协议.md) · [10-用户与存档](../需求/10-用户与存档.md) · [15-动态出口与通话中工具事件](../需求/15-动态出口与通话中工具事件.md) · [18-部署拓扑与BS架构](./18-部署拓扑与BS架构.md) · [**23-引擎存取Port与IO适配**](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)\n\n本文把宿主生命周期、会话 schema、磁盘布局、Free 挂机管线、媒介时序、幂等、锁决策、错误码与日志等**拍板定稿**；与早期仅概念描述冲突时以本文为准，并回写对应需求文。\n\n**存取：** Host 经注入的 Content / Profile / Memory / EngineLog Port 访问工作区；磁盘布局由 IO 模块解释。本机实现见 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`（详见 [23](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)）。\n\n---\n\n## 1. EngineHost（进程单例）\n\n### 1.1 形态\n\n```text\nNext server 启动\n  → createEngineIOPorts(dataRoot)     # Studio：engineIOModule\n  → createEngineHost({ ...ports })    # 进程单例\n  → loadWorkspace（经 ContentPort）\n  → 内存：profiles 缓存、sessionsByUserId、log ring buffer\n请求\n  → 门面注入 userId（来自 UserGate 选定后的开发态 cookie/header）\n  → host.xxx(...)\nendCall / 显式 save\n  → ProfilePort / MemoryPort 持久化（非引擎内直写 fs）\n```\n- **v1 不做**每请求 new Engine、不做多 Host 实例。\n- 未来 Web 多登录可按登录身份建实例；本阶段不预留复杂工厂。\n- 同 `userId` **同时最多 1 个**活跃 CallSession（`in_call`…`executing_effects`）；第二通 `beginCall` → `CONFLICT_ACTIVE_CALL`。\n- **Content 热重载 ≠ 清运行时**：编辑保存后 `loadWorkspace` / Studio `reloadStudioWorkspace` 只刷包缓存；`sessions` / `profiles` / `activeByUser` 默认保留。本通仍用 `frozenCard`（需求 03 §10）。踢会话走 `resetRuntime`（或 `loadWorkspace(..., { resetRuntime: true })`），禁与普通保存绑定。\n\n### 1.2 对外 API（实现级收敛）\n\n```ts\ninterface EngineHost {\n  /** 默认 resetRuntime=false：只刷 Content；显式 true 才清 Session/Profile */\n  loadWorkspace(rootDir: string, opts?: { resetRuntime?: boolean }): Promise<void>\n  /** 踢会话 + 清 Profile 缓存；禁与 Content 保存绑定 */\n  resetRuntime(): void\n  /** 规则在引擎；读包经 ContentPort.loadPackageForValidate（见 23 §7） */\n  validatePackage(packageId: string): ValidationReport\n\n  listUsers(): UserSummary[]\n  createUser(input: CreateUserInput): Promise<User>\n  deleteUser(userId: string): Promise<void>\n  /** 门禁选定后，后续 API 带此上下文或显式传 userId；落盘经 ProfilePort */\n  ensureProfile(userId: string): Promise<PlayerProfile>\n  saveProfile(userId: string, reason: SaveReason): Promise<void>\n\n  resolve(userId: string, intent: CallIntent): ResolveResult | EngineError\n  beginCall(userId: string, result: ResolveResult, opts: BeginCallOpts): CallSession\n  registerExitCandidate(sessionId: string, candidate: RuntimeExitCandidate): void\n  endCall(sessionId: string, outcome: Outcome): EndCallResult\n\n  getSnapshot(userId: string): EngineSnapshot\n  advanceClock(userId: string, ms: number): void\n  getRecentLogs(opts?: { userId?: string; limit?: number }): LogRecord[]\n}\n\ntype SaveReason = \"after_effect\" | \"after_free_pipeline\" | \"manual\" | \"autosave\"","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":531,"fileSize":22479,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":60},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-5156ac2c-1d36-4580-a80b-7f6f97c3e965-32\nfc_84704f4b-a054-9a83-b992-408f0f83f98a_5","startedAtMs":"1784786590155","completedAtMs":"1784786590325"},"model_call_id":"37c577a3-d489-4424-8aef-203754da5572-6-711l","session_id":"af9c32ce-fb63-495c-a8c5-233eb47f1680","timestamp_ms":1784786590601}
